Demonstration Manual :

press "Jouer" to play
use joystick to control ship
press 'F' to fire
press 'N' to select nearest enemy
press 'S' to select next target (friend and foe)
press 'P' to select previous target
press 'Escape' to quit

Dependencies : 

Actual version depends on following modules/libraries : 

  - Ogre 3d (www.ogre3d.org)
  - OIS (http://www.wreckedgames.com/wiki/index.php/WreckedLibs:OIS)
  - CppUnit (http://sourceforge.net/projects/cppunit)
  - RLog (http://arg0.net/wiki/rlog)
  - ODE (http://)
  - boost ... (http://

File descriptions :

- Doxyfile : configuration file for doxygen
- sources : sources directory, sources are organised in a "java" manner; .h 
  files location corresponds to namespace declaration, e.g., namespace 
  ProjetUnivers::Kernel correpsond to sources/kernel.     
- sources/artificial_intelligence : automatic pilot
- sources/kernel : mvc framework and utilities
- sources/display : display module
- sources/demonstration : demo program
- sources/gui : menus...
- sources/input : keyboard, joystick ... input handling 
- sources/model : game internal model representing all game data 
- sources/physic : physic module
- sources/sound : sound module
- sources/artificial_intelligence : AI module
